
<main>
    <div id="carouselId" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-bs-target="#carouselId" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-bs-target="#carouselId" data-bs-slide-to="1"></li>
            <li data-bs-target="#carouselId" data-bs-slide-to="2"></li>
            <li data-bs-target="#carouselId" data-bs-slide-to="3"></li>
        </ol>
        <div class="carousel-inner mb-3" role="listbox">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="/images/home/slide/WEB-LEN.jpg" alt="First slide">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="/images/home/slide/WEB.jpg" alt="Second slide">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="/images/home/slide/slide3.jpg" alt="Third slide">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="/images/home/slide/slide4.jpg" alt="Four slide">
            </div>
        </div>
        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselId" data-bs-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
        </button>
        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselId" data-bs-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
            </button>
    </div>
</main>
<section class="hero-banner bg-light py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-5 offset-lg-1 order-lg-1">
                <img src="/images/banner/banner_3.jpg" class="img-fluid" alt="Web Development">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h1 class="mt-3" style="font-size: 80px;">Fasshion and so much more</h1>
                <p class="lead text-secondary my-5">
                    Thời trang  <span style="font-weight: bold;">H4T</span>   mang phong cách thời trang đặc trưng Pháp sang trọng, thanh lịch và quyến rũ từ các bộ trang phục công sở nhẹ nhàng đến các bộ bộ thời trang tuổi Teen, dạ hội, dạo phố...
                </p>
                <a href="/web/san_pham" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg border">Xem ngay</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<div class="card mt-3">
    <h2 class="card-header" style="text-align: center;">Sản phẩm nổi bật</h2>
    <div class="card-body ">
        <div class="row">
            {{#each san_pham}}
                <div class="col-3 card_item" >
                    <div class="card mb-3 ">
                        <div class="card_img">
                            <img src="/images/product/p{{id_sp}}/{{id_sp}}.png" class="card-img-top" alt="{{ten_sp}}" title="{{ten_sp}} : {{gia_sp}}">
                            <a class="btn btn-dark quick_view" href="/web/views_sp/{{id_sp}}" role="button"> <i class="fas fa-eye"></i> Quick view</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                                <h5 class="card-title">{{ten_sp}}</h5>
                                 {{#if giam_gia_sp}}
                                    <h4 class="card-text" style="color: rgb(218, 109, 109);" >{{f_giam_gia_sp}}</h4>
                                {{/if}}
                            </div>
                            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                                {{#if giam_gia_sp}}
                                    <h6 class="card-text" style="color: black; text-decoration: line-through; " >{{f_gia_sp}}</h6> 
                                {{/if}}
                                <h6 class="card-text" style="color: rgb(120, 120, 202);" >{{gia_moi}}</h6>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>  
                </div>  
            {{/each}}
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

